{"tid":2224780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警罵「你老母」沙展睇片稱講「你有冇」","createTime":"2020-09-30T19:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T14:39:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":542,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"4a6353a4615e8ccb5a03ecbce76f71c7923a62a6","tid":2224780,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T19:16:45.000Z","msg":"19歲青年被指去年10月1日在荃灣示威，從行人天橋上向警察掟磚，被控非法集結罪，昨日受審。辯方播放傳媒片段，直指截查被告的警署警長證供不盡不實，例如被告遭搜查時，有警察責罵「有手套，你老母」，警署警長起初否認，播片聽到此句後仍不同意，只隱約聽到「手套，你有冇」，堅稱聽不到辯方「講嗰個粗俗嘅意思」。<br />\n<br />\n警署警長劉世明供稱，當日被告趙嘉進（19歲）穿白衣，與兩名黑衣人在荃新天地外的天橋上掟磚。劉與同僚上前處理，被告等人退到一群黑衣人身後，警方開始掃蕩時，黑衣人走往法院方向，被告其間轉為跑向荃新天地，在鎖上的商場門前扔下護目鏡、帽、豬嘴和手套，終被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指截查被告時，劉或其他警員曾說「有手套，你老母」、「你好寸喎」，並叫被告跪地，而劉曾說「向你指出個豬嘴係你㗎嘛」。劉否認說過或聽到這些語句，亦沒人命令被告跪低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/USQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FUSQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=d2687baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FUSQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U%2F&h=aac91879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/USQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U/</a>"},{"pid":"06e92f7280905f3126d7f98abb370aa890767739","tid":2224780,"uid":305767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T19:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e2e9dd65a7e88894e46092f1a3725a5bd521dd0","tid":2224780,"uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"06e92f7280905f3126d7f98abb370aa890767739","tid":2224780,"uid":305767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T19:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />