1T03:21:50.000Z","msg":"達哥啲Fd 嚟㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mxgOOzA57L0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmxgOOzA57L0&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=22854bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mxgOOzA57L0</a>"},{"pid":"14a06c0a5b3b26fbcdcd366465c576513c16b2a8","tid":2224780,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"咁又係 狗冇老母既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3052fd757c4ab4881496d1abd19e409aa8884e","tid":2224780,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>19歲青年被指去年10月1日在荃灣示威，從行人天橋上向警察掟磚，被控非法集結罪，昨日受審。辯方播放傳媒片段，直指截查被告的警署警長證供不盡不實，例如被告遭搜查時，有警察責罵「有手套，你老母」，警署警長起初否認，播片聽到此句後仍不同意，只隱約聽到「手套，你有冇」，堅稱聽不到辯方「講嗰個粗俗嘅意思」。<br />\n<br />\n警署警長劉世明供稱，當日被告趙嘉進（19歲）穿白衣，與兩名黑衣人在荃新天地外的天橋上掟磚。劉與同僚上前處理，被告等人退到一群黑衣人身後，警方開始掃蕩時，黑衣人走往法院方向，被告其間轉為跑向荃新天地，在鎖上的商場門前扔下護目鏡、帽、豬嘴和手套，終被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指截查被告時，劉或其他警員曾說「有手套，你老母」、「你好寸喎」，並叫被告跪地，而劉曾說「向你指出個豬嘴係你㗎嘛」。劉否認說過或聽到這些語句，亦沒人命令被告跪低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/USQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FUSQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=d2687baa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FUSQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U%2F&h=aac91879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/USQVSKNSLFDSJA2PRL7HEAFX6U/</a></blockquote><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">正一&quot;趴街咸蝦燦&quot;！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1b12ba00eea792a0f0217d5399c